    <item>
      <title>加沙中部袭击事件后以色列军队释放四名人质</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-08/israeli-forces-free-four-hostages-after-attack-in-central-gaza</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列军方于周六在对中部城市努塞拉特发动大规模攻击时，释放了被哈马斯关押在加沙地带的四名人质。哈马斯控制的政府媒体办公室称，至少有 210 名巴勒斯坦人在激烈战斗中丧生，其中包括儿童。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-08/israeli-forces-free-four-hostages-after-attack-in-central-gaza</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 11:20:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>袭击丹麦首相后，男子被判入狱并受到指控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-08/danish-prime-minister-cancels-eu-election-events-after-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名 39 岁的男子因袭击丹麦首相梅特·弗雷德里克森并导致其取消多次选举活动而被监禁，并被指控对官员实施暴力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-08/danish-prime-minister-cancels-eu-election-events-after-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 08:53:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受制裁的大亨将在保加利亚选举中扮演权力掮客</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-08/bulgaria-elections-sanctioned-mogul-set-to-be-kingmaker-in-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[保加利亚即将举行三年来的第六次选举，要想摆脱该国长期的政治僵局，可能需要一名因腐败而受到制裁的权力掮客。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-08/bulgaria-elections-sanctioned-mogul-set-to-be-kingmaker-in-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其将对所有中国汽车加征 40% 关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-08/turkey-to-impose-additional-40-tariff-on-all-china-vehicles</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其将对所有从中国购买的汽车征收 40% 的关税，以抑制进口并缩小经常账户赤字。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-08/turkey-to-impose-additional-40-tariff-on-all-china-vehicles</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 06:44:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲极右翼不顾失误，力争举行横幅选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-08/european-elections-2024-eu-far-right-seeks-banner-election-despite-mishaps</link>
      <description><![CDATA[预计欧洲极右翼政党将在周日的议会选举中取得可观的胜利。但内斗和丑闻让一些民族主义团体陷入混乱，这可能会限制他们的政治影响力，并给仍有望赢得绝对多数的主流政党一些喘息空间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-08/european-elections-2024-eu-far-right-seeks-banner-election-despite-mishaps</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>调查显示，受挫的莫迪领导的印度人民党在印度农村地区失利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-08/chastened-modi-s-bjp-lost-ground-in-rural-india-survey-suggests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项调查显示，农村选票的波动导致选举受挫，使得总理纳伦德拉·莫迪不得不依靠联盟来治理印度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-08/chastened-modi-s-bjp-lost-ground-in-rural-india-survey-suggests</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 05:37:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>保守党长期担心的时刻终于来临</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-08/sunak-s-conservative-campaign-in-disarray-after-farage-entry-d-day-blunder</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 在 7 月 4 日之后继续担任英国首相的希望渺茫，但在经历了一周的危机之后，这一希望似乎破灭了：一个是他以为自己可以避免的危机，而另一个则注定会成为他自己犯下的历史性大错。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-08/sunak-s-conservative-campaign-in-disarray-after-farage-entry-d-day-blunder</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京在乌克兰问题上取得突破的时间已经不多了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-08/putin-is-running-out-of-time-to-achieve-breakthrough-in-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[几个月来，俄罗斯军队在与缺乏武器和弹药的乌克兰军队的战场上只取得了有限的进展。随着俄罗斯军队的优势开始减弱，这对总统弗拉基米尔·普京来说是一个越来越大的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-08/putin-is-running-out-of-time-to-achieve-breakthrough-in-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民意调查显示法拉奇是继苏纳克之后担任保守党领袖的首选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-08/poll-suggests-nigel-farage-top-pick-to-succeed-rishi-sunak-as-tory-leader</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项民意调查显示，如果工党赢得大选，改革英国的奈杰尔·法拉奇是接替首相里希·苏纳克担任保守党领袖的最受欢迎人选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-08/poll-suggests-nigel-farage-top-pick-to-succeed-rishi-sunak-as-tory-leader</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 04:57:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
